<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 12:26:37 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>由于欧盟和美国关税的影响，电动汽车公司 Lotus Tech 大幅下调年度交付量预测</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/ev-firm-lotus-tech-slashes-annual-deliveries-forecast-eu-us-tariffs-weigh-2024-08-28/</link><description>电动汽车公司 Lotus Technology 周三将今年的交付量预期下调了 50% 以上，理由是美国和欧盟的新关税带来了不确定性。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 12:04:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/ev-firm-lotus-tech-slashes-annual-deliveries-forecast-eu-us-tariffs-weigh-2024-08-28/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟和中国启动促进工业数据流动的机制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/eu-china-launch-mechanism-facilitate-industrial-data-flows-2024-08-28/</link><description>欧盟在周三的一份声明中表示，欧盟和中国在旨在简化跨境数据流动的新体系下启动了首次讨论。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 11:38:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/eu-china-launch-mechanism-facilitate-industrial-data-flows-2024-08-28/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，制药商萌蒂的中国业务出售未能找到买家</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/drugmaker-mundipharmas-china-unit-sale-fails-find-buyer-sources-say-2024-08-28/</link><description>两位知情人士称，亿万富翁萨克勒家族旗下的制药商萌蒂国际制药公司在今年的重新出售过程中第二次未能为其中国子公司找到买家。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 11:04:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/drugmaker-mundipharmas-china-unit-sale-fails-find-buyer-sources-say-2024-08-28/</guid></item><item><title>汉莎航空首席财务官表示，汉莎航空在跨大西洋主要市场受到竞争挤压</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/lufthansa-squeezed-by-competition-key-transatlantic-market-says-cfo-2024-08-28/</link><description>德国航空公司首席财务官告诉记者，由于来自中国和美国竞争对手的竞争日益激烈，汉莎航空在其主要的跨大西洋市场面临机票价格下跌的问题。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 10:50:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/lufthansa-squeezed-by-competition-key-transatlantic-market-says-cfo-2024-08-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪利润增长33%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-electric-vehicle-giant-byds-first-half-profit-jumps-244-2024-08-28/</link><description>中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪周三公布第二季度净利润增长 32.8%，这是自 2023 年底以来的最快增长，尽管全球最大汽车市场的大件支出步履蹒跚。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 10:47:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-electric-vehicle-giant-byds-first-half-profit-jumps-244-2024-08-28/</guid></item><item><title>英国人韦斯特伍德被任命为香港新任主教练</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/englishman-westwood-named-new-hong-kong-head-coach-2024-08-28/</link><description>中国足协周三宣布，前阿富汗主教练阿什利·韦斯特伍德已被任命为香港队主教练。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 10:38:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/englishman-westwood-named-new-hong-kong-head-coach-2024-08-28/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：正如英伟达等待的那样，美国国债吸收了新的洪流</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-08-28/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 10:07:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-08-28/</guid></item><item><title>香港开发商押注中国需求，转向租赁市场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/betting-chinese-demand-hong-kong-developers-turn-rental-market-2024-08-28/</link><description>一些香港开发商现在转向住房租赁和租赁市场，以应对房地产市场的长期低迷，并满足中国内地专业人士和学生不断增长的租赁需求。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 08:05:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/betting-chinese-demand-hong-kong-developers-turn-rental-market-2024-08-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国滴滴出行将成为四维图新第二大股东</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-didi-become-2nd-largest-shareholder-state-backed-navinfo-unit-2024-08-28/</link><description>周三，四维图新在一份证券交易所文件中表示，中国网约车巨头滴滴出行将用现金加上其智能驾驶和座舱部门收购车行科技 16.5% 的股份。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 07:55:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-didi-become-2nd-largest-shareholder-state-backed-navinfo-unit-2024-08-28/</guid></item><item><title>又有两家中国航空公司开始运营中国商飞C919客机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/two-more-chinese-airlines-start-flying-china-made-comac-c919-jet-2024-08-28/</link><description>据官方媒体中央电视台报道，国航和南航周三接收首架飞机后，将成为第二家和第三家运营中国商飞 C919 客机的中国航空公司。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 07:11:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/two-more-chinese-airlines-start-flying-china-made-comac-c919-jet-2024-08-28/</guid></item><item><title>澳门法官宣布竞逐世界最大赌场中心</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/macau-judge-announces-bid-lead-worlds-biggest-casino-hub-2024-08-28/</link><description>澳门高级法官岑豪辉周三宣布，他打算在 10 月份竞选澳门行政长官，因为世界上最大的赌博中心正在努力将自己转变为主要的区域旅游目的地。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 03:42:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/macau-judge-announces-bid-lead-worlds-biggest-casino-hub-2024-08-28/</guid></item><item><title>随着英伟达盈利临近，股价稳定在历史最高点附近</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-28/</link><description>周三，在芯片制造市场宠儿英伟达公布业绩之前，全球股市保持在历史高点附近，而英镑则徘徊在 2-1/2 年高点附近，因为交易员押注英国在降息方面将落后于美国。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 02:22:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-28/</guid></item><item><title>据央视报道，中美讨论拜登和习近平新一轮会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-holds-2nd-day-talks-taiwan-fentanyl-with-top-biden-aide-2024-08-28/</link><description>中国官方媒体周三称，在中国最高外交官王毅在北京会见美国国家安全顾问杰克·沙利文后，中美高级官员讨论了在不久的将来举行两国元首新的会谈。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 02:17:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-holds-2nd-day-talks-taiwan-fentanyl-with-top-biden-aide-2024-08-28/</guid></item><item><title>据 The Information 报道，TikTok 内容战略主管将离职</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktoks-head-content-strategy-leave-information-reports-2024-08-27/</link><description>据 The Information 周二援引发给员工的通知报道，TikTok 内容战略和政策主管 Nicole Iacopetti 将于 9 月 6 日离开公司。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 21:31:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktoks-head-content-strategy-leave-information-reports-2024-08-27/</guid></item><item><title>网络安全公司称，中国黑客利用漏洞危害互联网公司</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/chinese-hackers-exploited-bug-compromise-internet-companies-cybersecurity-firm-2024-08-27/</link><description>一家网络安全公司周二表示，一个中国黑客组织利用一个软件漏洞危害了美国和海外的多家互联网公司。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 16:38:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/chinese-hackers-exploited-bug-compromise-internet-companies-cybersecurity-firm-2024-08-27/</guid></item></channel></rss>